By: Bâyazid al-Bistâmî
---
Even when you see a man endowed with miraculous powers to the point of rising
in the air, do not let yourself be deluded, but investigate whether he observes
the divine precepts and prohibitions, whether he stays within the limits of
religion and whether he accomplishes the duties this imposes upon him.
